{"tid":1982810,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救，開唔著機，底板/火牛問題","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T12:12:11.000Z","uid":177036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64b5e63666240eeb43d7d61477d6c5cbac8d3734","tid":1982810,"uid":177036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"電腦一直用開，突然開唔著求救，跪求幫幫忙<br />\n<br />\n部desktop插電著電源，底板燈就著一著，根住熄返，禁機箱電源制無反應<br />\n<br />\n試過炆哂顯卡，USB 同其他device, 得條ram行機，情況一樣<br />\n<br />\n試過short隻牛，風扇可著<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩可以試知道邊part壞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd5ef40292ea6443eb01c3bc382274045596482","tid":1982810,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況不問原由都可以咁做<br />\n1. 換power cord、直插插蘇唔經拖板<br />\n2. Reset BIOS<br />\n3. 裸跑"}]}